<subSubSection id="D91423503F00A5928CC5874D06FE8ED0" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="notes">
<paragraph id="6AC13A82B3EEBAFE2E5A2A54DD6056D1" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="03653B6CFB3BF45582A56B1B4A403482" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distinguished by the relatively long bracteoles, the distinctive white, asperous-pilose indumentum, which is particularly prominent on the inflorescence, and by the characteristically compact inflorescence.</paragraph>
